import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import store from './store.js'
import 'bootstrap'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import router from './router/index.js'  

import './assets/css/style.css'

import '../src/assets/plugins/line-icons/line-icons.css'
import '../src/assets/plugins/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css'
import '../src/assets/plugins/flexslider/flexslider.css'
import '../src/assets/plugins/parallax-slider/css/parallax-slider.css'

import './assets/css/theme-colors/default.css'


/* import vuetify from './plugins/vuefity'*/


/*
import 'bootstrap'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import router from './router'
*/

createApp(App).use(router).use(store).mount('#app')
